nodes.text: The Albino Wyyyschokk was a rare subspecies of Wyyyschokk native to the planet Kashyyyk. Faster and more aggressive than normal Wyyyschokks, these massive spiders were found in dark, subterranean areas where they could live for centuries. The species was capable of spitting venom, which it used to disable its prey before feeding on their brains.
While exploring Kashyyyk, Cal Kestis was attacked by an Albino Wyyyschokk. He had to fight it off, eventually killing the creature.
